<dl id="n01022d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n01" href="#n01022d">N01 (VI.B.10)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n01all.htm#n01022d"> 22(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> martyr to indigestion <small>Brown</small></blockquote> <dd class="well"> <ul class="list-inline" id="n01022d"> <li><a href="../../flex/z/lexfh.htm#n01022d">FH VII</a> </li><li><ms href="#n01022d">MS NLI.FH-1r <a name="fhvii0d" href="../../ff/fdra/fhda.htm#fhvii0d">Usage</a></ms> </li><li> <a href="../../flex/z/fhvii0d.htm#n01022d">Draft: FHvii.0</a></li> </ul> <ul class="list-inline" id="n01022d"></li><li>FW 431.25 </li><li><a href="../../flex/qA/lexqA.htm#n01022d">2010</a> </li><li><a href="../../flex/qA/l39qA.htm#n01022d">1939</a> </li><li><ms href="#n01022d">MS BL 47482b-7</ms> </li><li>JJA 57:015 <a name="qA0d" href="../../ff/fdra/qda.htm#qA0d">Usage</a> </li><li> <a href="../../flex/q/qA0d.htm#n01022d">Draft: III&sect;2A.0</a></li> </ul> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[Author, Journalist &mdash; &amp; / Martyr to Indigestion]</font> Writing from St. Michael&apos;s House, Southhampton, Ernest Lawton, the well-known author and journalist, says:&mdash; &ldquo;For many years I was a <mark>martyr to indigestion</mark> and could get no relief <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> when a friend induced me to try Bisurated Magnesia, which, I am pleased to say, effected a complete and permanent cure. <small> <a name="SP29oct22" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#SP29oct22"><cite title="source">Sunday Express</cite></a> (29 October 1922) 15/1</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
